<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: HPJ-L01 Megawatt Particle Lance -->
  <CMC_Lasercannon.label>HPJ-L01 兆瓦级粒子光矛</CMC_Lasercannon.label>
  <!-- EN: Equipped with high-energy particle beam weapons, this turret fires focused particle rays capable of dealing massive damage to targets within short range. -->
  <CMC_Lasercannon.description>这些炮塔安装有高能粒子束武器，能够发射聚焦的粒子射线并对短距离内的目标造成巨幅伤害。</CMC_Lasercannon.description>
  
  <!-- EN: HPJ-L21 Gigawatt Particle Lance -->
  <CMC_Lasercannon_TEST.label>HPJ-L21 千兆级粒子光矛</CMC_Lasercannon_TEST.label>
  <!-- EN: A super-heavy energy weapon usually serving as a destroyer's secondary battery array. It fires focused particle rays that can penetrate shields and heavy armor, causing massive damage. It can fire over walls. -->
  <CMC_Lasercannon_TEST.description>通常作为驱逐舰副炮阵列的超重型能量武器，能够发射聚焦的粒子射线可以穿透护盾和重型装甲并造成巨幅伤害，可以越过墙体射击。</CMC_Lasercannon_TEST.description>
  
